{"tid":1552772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］手足小心 將軍澳地鐵站有防暴","createTime":"2019-09-08T11:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T14:13:54.000Z","uid":259776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5174f9573c45798f8075bf969d415347a16b9649","tid":1552772,"uid":259776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ED1LZAb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FED1LZAb.png&h=36c28927&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64b555d4312b5415fe8ba75a93b05e41146efa6d","tid":1552772,"uid":167163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:59:07.000Z","msg":"散仔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68470683d7ecc6a6cb76fa526ae733bdc27c1632","tid":1552772,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:00:45.000Z","msg":"轉發<br />\n我算係條隊嘅中游位，但臨上到美領有班狗set防線唔畀上，然後就有人舉牌話封左中環站，集會取消，唔畀上美領，要係16點30定45分前散。跟住一大班人上唔到美領，焗住落返中環。但中環同香港封站，又焗撚住去金鐘，點知沿途一路話金鐘站大量狗喎。金鐘站係轉地鐵出返去新界九龍嘅站，你佈撚晒防邊個敢去？現場好多人叫唔好坐黨鐵，結果成班走晒去等巴士，但巴士係絕對唔夠散，而且我仲見到班狗開始封路玩管制，即係連巴士都想搞埋。<br />\n我一路行，一路見到有d手足開始上gear，但佢地上完之後係企係原地等和理非散水，有d甚至走返去中環，如果唔係佢地拖時間，一大班和理非將會食tg甚至子彈放題。<br />\n知唔知今日幾多人得d爛鳩醫生口罩？想殺人呀？<br />\n今日係黑警有心玩野，唔好再屌前線。"},{"pid":"2fc07815e6415f21b767ca0d18405280a6244838","tid":1552772,"uid":259776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:13:54.000Z","msg":"九龍灣所有出口都有，各位小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4q8X7v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4q8X7v.png&h=101cd7e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N6Z9Hza.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN6Z9Hza.jpg&h=09ca4d95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXybbsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXybbsy.png&h=777f9553&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}